<div class="card p-4 mb-4">

    <h3 class="mb-3">Our Story</h3>

    <p>
        Petco Supplies is a small family-run pet shop that has proudly served
        pet owners for more than 40 years. Throughout the years, we've remained
        committed to providing quality products, friendly service, and expert
        advice to help keep pets happy and healthy.
    </p>

    <p>
        We stock a wide range of pet supplies including food, treats, toys,
        bedding, housing, and everyday essentials for many types of domestic pets.
        Whether you're welcoming a new companion or caring for a lifelong friend,
        we're here to help.
    </p>

</div>

